    <PrimAttribute name="isShiftMove" id="ba18711a-7b01-43a1-b319-26700d78b2f5">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>


#############################

THIS IS USED TO SHIFT 30, 45 ETC LEFT OR RIGHT IN THE GRID GRAPHIC

THIS IS ALSO USED TO TELL THE MOVE CONTROLLER THAT THE MOVE ORIGINATED FROM MOBILE UI. iT IS DOING THE SAME AS MYORIGINATINGFORM FROM THE HH</text>
