    <PrimAttribute name="isWoChangeOfTransportRelShip" id="5cf3a2b7-0179-4f96-a42b-2df64a31fa93">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>Used to stop the creation of a release ship and warfage transaction
When we are changing the transport mode of a work order the cargo sometimes need to be moved.
In this case we do not want to create a Release-Ship and Warfage transaction on the tis.
We just want to move the tis.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
