        <text>


This date was added because data like events and transactions needed to have a date time that is not 'now'. 
Passing the retrospective date through method calls, changing all the references to do this was a big job, that now is unecessary.

Set this date before the TRX. In the Finialize of the TRX it will be nulled.

A similar data is on CM_Passport, this is used for transactions as well, because not all transctions are created during a move.</text>
