/*
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
Created:			02 August 2002 by cnwdwq1
Purpose:			Sets the move index for planned or queued moves. If this is 0
							we will shift to end of array of CM_FutureMoves, else we move
							to where they request it to go. Default is at head (first)
